metadata.name: EXISTED Place
metadata.description:
Somewhere this place exists.
There time stops and nothing moves except the gray clouds overhead. You lie in a chair under the tree and reality eludes you. Where is it? Everyone has been to this place, everyone remembers it on a subconscious level.

A harmonious blend of peacefulness and hopelessness. 

Location type: Meditation zone
Location name: Existed Place
World name: UTOPIA 513
